explains: adj. 不满意的；不高兴的；流露不满的
v. 使不满（dissatisfy 的过去式和过去分词）

sentences.en: Did he mean (that) he was dissatisfied with our service?
sentences.cn: 他是不是表示对我们的服务不满意？

sentences.en: If you are dissatisfied with our service, please write to the manager.
sentences.cn: 对我们的服务如有不满，请函告经理。

sentences.en: Eighty-two percent of voters are dissatisfied with the way their country is being governed.
sentences.cn: 82%的投票者对他们国家的管理方式不满意。
